\nstep before the development of the CryoAC Demonstration Model (DM), which will\nbe the detector able to demonstrate the critical technologies expected in the\nCryoAC development programme.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 23 Jul 2018 12:34:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-07-24"}
