r methods are applied to\nonline underwater object detection and grasping with an autonomous system.\nCodes are publicly available at https://github.com/SeanChenxy/TDRN.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 23 Jul 2018 14:29:27 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 18 Sep 2018 01:06:52 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 17 Dec 2018 10:02:44 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 7 May 2019 13:55:18 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Sun, 22 Dec 2019 09:50:38 GMT"},{"version":"v6","created":"Fri, 13 Mar 2020 15:41:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-03-16"}
