age of preheating. It effectively produces the charged\nparticles, implementing the Schwinger reheating scenario even before the fast\noscillations of the inflaton. The numerical analysis is carried out in the\nStarobinsky model of inflation for the powerlike $f\\propto a^{\\alpha}$ and\nRatra-type $f=\\exp(\\beta\\phi/M_{p})$ coupling functions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 22 Jul 2018 22:01:11 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 27 Sep 2018 08:15:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-10-03"}
